	<summary>
	3/25/1994--Introduced.
21st Century Community Learning Centers Act - Directs the Secretary of Education to make grants to rural and inner city public schools or consortia for projects that benefit the educational, health, social security, cultural, and recreational needs of rural or inner city communities. Authorizes appropriations.

	</summary>
